Description: Metabolomics Workbench is one of the main public repositories for
    storage of metabolomics experiments. The MsBackendMetabolomicsWorkbench
    package provides functionality to retrieve and represent mass spectrometry
    (MS) data from Metabolomics Workbench. Data files are downloaded and cached
    locally avoiding repetitive downloads. MS data from metabolomics experiments
    can thus be directly and seamlessly integrated into R-based analysis
    workflows with the Spectra and MsBackendMetabolomicsWorkbench package.
